      Hotels in Ooty

      With a beautiful nature background and pleasant weather, Ooty is a place to must-visit. This hill station is located in the Nilgiri Hills in the state of Tamil Nadu. It is a popular city among honeymoon couples, families and youngsters. People who like camping and enjoying nature are mostly welcomed to this place. Apart from nature’s blessings, Ooty has magnificent landmarks that tempts the tourists to visit here. It is a well-developed city with modern accommodation facilities. And through Goibibo, booking hotels in Ooty have become an easier task. There are several must-visit places like Ooty Boat House, St. Stephen’s Church, and Kalhatti Falls. Goibibo easily filters out the best results of Ooty hotels near these landmarks.

      Families and couples looking for a luxurious memorable stay at this holiday destination have a number of best hotels in Ooty to choose from. Some of the hand-picked hotels for families in Ooty are Shaliha Mist View, Hotel Lakeview Ooty, and British Cliff Club Resort. And if you cannot afford stays under high taris then there are plenty of hotels available at reasonable prices as well. La Flora Amberley Resort, Aurora Light Residency, Wyoming Heritage Bungalow, Garden Manor, Pebrock Heritage Inn and Hotel Fairstay are known for medium range tariffs, friendly hospitality and good rooms in Ooty.

      If you are not fond of 5 star hotels and exaggerated facilities but like suitable facilities under a decent price with decent facilities then 3 star hotels in Ooty would be optimum for you. The hotels under this category include Al-Woodlands Residency, Western Valley Resorts, Garden Manor, Fortune Retreats and more. Budget hotels in Ooty booking has become much easier with Goibibo as you can pick from numerous accommodations that suits your requirements.

      For transit travellers who need rooms that cost low tariffs, budget hotels in ooty are good options. Hotel Alakapuri, Rose Park Residency, Tulips Valley View Resorts, Green Moon Residency, Hotel Landmark, RN Holidays and more.

      If you are looking for hotels in ooty near bus stand then Hotel Maneck, Hotel Raja, Mount View Heritage Hotel, Green Apple Residence, Raasinihas Paradise and more hotels in this area would be good for a comfortable stay.

      For honeymoon couples, a romantic background with candlelight dinner is a must requirement. Some of the best hotels for couples in Ooty are Rose Park Residency at Garden Road, La Blooms, Kumaran Cottage and Hotel Golden City at Coonoor Road, Shaliha Mist View at Kodanad Road, Glen Park Inn, Hotel Sapphire Grand and I-India at Charring Cross.

      Looking for luxury in Ooty amidst nature? There are resorts are here with a palate of first-class services and grand architecture. Accord Highland Ooty, Sinclairs Retreat Ooty, Sterling Ooty Elk Hill, Fortune Resort Sullivan Court-Member ITC Hotel Group and Tulips Elkhill Resorts on Elk Hill are splendid stay accommodations. And if Villa is your theme of accommodation then, Modern Villa at Bombay Castle would be perfect. Not only villas and resorts give the peace of mind people come to seek here, but cottages also provide the rural-like adventure and best-ever amenities. Some of the top-notch cottages are Rainbow Cottage at Club Road, Lakshmi Cottage, and Eadenz Cottage in Davisdale.

      Popular chain hotels are Vinayaga Inn by Poppys Hotel, Hotel Mayura Sudarshan Ooty, Sterling Ooty Fern Hill, Zostel Ooty, and Club Mahindra Derby Green. Vinayaga Inn by Poppys is a two-star hotel on Garden Road with amenities like Bar, Restaurant, and free parking. Hotel Lakeview, on the other hand, is a spacious hotel with green surroundings and a superb lake view with fantastic amenities.

      Some tourists like solidarity and prefer distant hotels and villas while some like mingling with people. For those penny-saving extrovert backpackers, homestays and B&Bs are perfect stay choices. Holiday Home near Ooty Lake, Ooty White House Homestay, Greenyards, Seven Hill Homestay are good homestays to consider.

      Just like the places of interest are breathtaking, the cuisine here is very tantalising too. Idli, Dosa, Vada, Sambhar are famous dishes. Home-made chocolates, white chocolates, cakes and buns are a dream come true for sweet lovers. Some of the best restaurants in Ooty are Place to Bee, Earl’s Secret, Club Mahindra Danish Villa, and Angaara Multicuisine Restaurant. 

      If you are looking for cottages then Goibibo has wide range of Ooty Hotels of cottages category like Rainbow Cottage Ooty, Mountain Trails Ooty and Hotel Sweekar Residency Ooty. Similarly you can check some of 4 star category hotels in Ooty like Sterling Ooty Elk Hill, Sterling Ooty Fern Hill and Fortune Resort Sullivan Court Ooty. But if you are Couple Friendly Option then you can choose to stay in Ooty Hotels like Darshan Hotel Ooty, Glen Park Inn and Hotel Lakeview Ooty. In terms of food, Ooty has a plethora of restaurants serving lip-smacking food, some popular Ooty Hotels with in-house restaurants are The Majestic Crown, Fortune Retreats Ooty and Hotel Sanjay Ooty. It is always recommended to choose your stay after checking reviews posted by our fellow travelers. Some top reviewed Ooty Hotels at Goibibo are Kumaran Cottage Ooty, Accord HighLand Ooty and Vinayaga Inn by Poppys Ooty. You can also choose your stay from certified GoStays like Al-Woodlands Residency, Hotel Sri Balaji Ooty and Hotel Fairstay Ooty, all these Ooty Hotels have free Wi-Fi, AC, clean rooms and come with 100% money back guarantee in case there is customer dissatisfaction with respect to any of our commitments.

      Picking your best hotel from hundreds of options through Goibibo app will certainly make your Ooty trip a memorable one. Remember to read reviews and ratings before finalising your stay.

      There are few more popular cities near Ooty, which travellers also visit while visiting Ooty. Some of these are Mysore, Bangalore, Coorg, Mangalore, Coimbatore and Alleppey. You can find huge variety of Hotels in these cities on Goibibo platform right from Budget Hotels to Luxury Hotels.
